  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"prose style:1\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows two blocks on a semicircular track. The first block is located at the bottom of the track. The second block is located near the top left side of the track, at a vertical height of uppercase H from the bottom of the track.\" src=\"/images/205fa5e1e6b5349f7680a3d23701936a.svg\"></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">In Scenario <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span>, a block is placed at the bottom of a semicircular track, as shown. An identical block, released from rest at a height <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"uppercase H\"><math alttext=\"uppercase H\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>H</mi></math></span></span> above the bottom of the track, slides down and collides elastically with the block at the bottom of the track. The block at the bottom then slides up the track and reaches a maximum height <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"h sub max\"><math alttext=\"h sub max\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>h</mi><mi>max</mi></msub></math></span></span>. There is negligible friction between the blocks and the track. In Scenario <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span>, the process is repeated except the blocks stick together when they collide. Which of the following correctly indicates the maximum height that the bottom block reaches in Scenario <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span>?</p>\n",
    "answer": "i4",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Greater than <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"h sub max\"><math alttext=\"h sub max\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>h</mi><mi>max</mi></msub></math></span></span></p>",
        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Equal to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"h sub max\"><math alttext=\"h sub max\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>h</mi><mi>max</mi></msub></math></span></span></p>",
        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Equal to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"one half h sub max\"><math alttext=\"one half h sub max\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msub><mi>h</mi><mi>max</mi></msub></math></span></span></p>",
